documents.title: Fun & Hobbies
documents.content: I love baking and experimenting with all kinds of sweet treats. Some of my favorites include rainbow cakes, strawberry cakes, cupcakes, fudges, brownies, mousse, birthday cakes, and two-layer cakes. I enjoy exploring new flavors, decorating each creation with care, and sharing them with friends and family. Baking is not just a hobby for me—it’s a creative outlet that allows me to combine flavors, textures, and colors to make each dessert special and memorable.
